Between levels 1–4, PB is +2
Between levels 5–8, PB is +3
Between levels 9–12, PB is +4
Between levels 13–16, PB is +5
Between levels 16–20, PB is +6

For Wizards, Fighters, and Rogues your spellcasting ability modifier is Intelligence.
For Clerics, Druids, Rangers, and Monks  your SAM is Wisdom.
For Bards, Paladins, Sorcerers, and Warlocks your SAM is Charisma.

When you cast a spell, your spell attack modifier is:
Spellcasting Ability Modifier (SAM) + Proficiency Bonus (Prof. or PB)